00:09:04.942 --> 00:09:09.913
Now with this kind of self-paced
mastery base learning software,

00:09:09.913 --> 00:09:14.036
we were approached by the Los Altos
School District not to far from here,

00:09:14.036 --> 00:09:15.661
"What would you do with a classroom?"

00:09:17.522 --> 00:09:20.217
We said, "Well we would let every
